title: He Jumped Off The Golden Gate Bridge And Lived To Inspire!
description:
Kevin Hines is an American suicide prevention speaker, who gained nationwide fame in the United States for surviving an attempt at taking his own life by jumping from the Golden Gate Bridge in San Francisco. We are so luck to have him on the podcast today. Genuinely kind, funny, and has saved countless lives. We Hope we can get through to someone struggling today.
